SourceString: What do you wish to be?
I create essence which resists the ruin.
Knowledge is Lost, All is Lost.
Your words remind me of something.
Watch out where you bounce to!

Do you exist outside of my mind?
The unexamined life is not worth living!
The mind is furnished with ideas by a drunk upholsterer...
I'm the daughter of the Wizard!
I'm the daughter of the Wizard!
What is it like down there? Heh?
